{"tid":43913,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"考完試後出篇 Non Jupas 玩法分享","createTime":"2016-12-17T20:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T23:28:45.000Z","uid":14170,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2c1309ca4fc758f3a1d0826fbd7e597fb1da10db","tid":43913,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T20:38:42.000Z","msg":"最近收到風，原來真係有人打 Non jupas PS 竟然打成千字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇黎鏗哥真係要出馬教精你班 asso / hd 仔 Nonjupas 玩法係點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時唔係話寫得多字就得，要理解代入人地既情境去做佢想你做既野架 Ching <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 出 interview 俾你果個只係大學 admission office 既小職員，根據開會所得既 cut off (唔同 subdegree 唔同分數) 由高至低派 interview (除左 city 會西走高分既之外基本都係咁)，即係你份 PS 根本唔會影響你會唔會收到 interview <br />\n<br />\n2. Prof. 係當日 in 你前五分鐘，甚至係果一刻，先會收到你 application system 所打既資料，你想人地點樣係五分鐘內睇你成千字呀 Ching <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇你一個點睇哂十幾個呀，花咁多精神我晏啲仲點寫論文交數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醒目既 250 字係極限 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. PS 都係圍繞講返自己好啲，N 展 / 商科好多人講咩比賽又咩又盛，寫左幾百字都寫唔哂，你都係搞掂你自己先啦，篇野個主角係你唔係個比賽。<br />\n咩比賽，比賽要你做咩，三四句講完，重點要放係個比賽點樣令到你咁屈機，令到佢要收你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 重點放返係你自己<br />\n你一味寫廢話無人想睇，除非你屈機到寫到同佢同一個水平既論文<br />\n<br />\n4. PS 唔洗點提你係 Asso / HD 學過咩 course ，佢自己都有教大學 year1 / 2，大概估到學咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者你會有同學同佢講左，所以都請將個重點放返係你自己<br />\n<br />\nPS 大概都係咁寫，行文流暢睇得舒服就好夠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n字海我一望到已經唔想睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n詳細內容 (interview 心得) 等我考完試再講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：2012 Nonjupas 報左四間 U，HKU CU UST Poly 1st round 收哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ed31a2bd656c6f7b84d7e48ac761c6c91eb70a","tid":43913,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T20:43:58.000Z","msg":"最好就先寫 4-500 字，然後試下慢慢縮短到 250 - 300 字左右就 Ok"},{"pid":"ce209c7c53533718533aec6353d5db90ffad92ee","tid":43913,"uid":17167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T20:45:30.000Z","msg":"呢d照計一月間間asso都有talk教寫personal statement🤔"},{"pid":"06fc9d8bd99156eddba3f37b09e307edd03f35f5","tid":43913,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T20:46:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢d照計一月間間asso都有talk教寫personal statement🤔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIVE 無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00724a10fb94ab1b3eb211101d3085ff93c8059","tid":43913,"uid":62772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T20:46:28.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"68f58c5c77bd951d8b5a897d0b477f1546ae5ffc","tid":43913,"uid":17167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T20:47:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢d照計一月間間asso都有talk教寫personal statement🤔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIVE 無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLet's collab, 我出過PS flow/interview開場白flow 比朋友參考 佢地都覺得幾好用"},{"pid":"40a4847bf1b26a896f62b39791292b919c650a39","tid":43913,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T20:48:20.000Z","msg":"上年有 HD 學生入 CUHK HKUST <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗我都信得過既"},{"pid":"0ef6b8062b8ae350447620e59c89823c2011f1c1","tid":43913,"uid":17167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T20:49:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上年有 HD 學生入 CUHK HKUST <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗我都信得過既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCU好似好易升，有朋友space唔過三都升左中大"},{"pid":"4c3cf74ac9990abb6e17fad03e9e1d7befcc5c0b","tid":43913,"uid":14170,