al/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n12年？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc"},{"pid":"7fd246ace3f5d8b3e095c614c1d19d539fd4c571","tid":43913,"uid":9253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:40:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Gpa 3 頭 係咪唔洗諗入番ugc ? Ive商科</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNo, IVE 898</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n入比你睇 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c87acb3c02909138842c4ba9f18ab682c903cb16","tid":43913,"uid":24030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:56:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Gpa 3 頭 係咪唔洗諗入番ugc ? Ive商科</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  3.4 無ugc收 路過 <br />\n應該話連interview既機會都無</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇報水泡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65e4ad0fba45aa7b5c713c6bd4c45b94e42b65f","tid":43913,"uid":64441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T14:18:35.000Z","msg":"me  3.57爛英文grade 有冇機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e32d51cf44af693e9b9d679389460ee7065ed82","tid":43913,"uid":17167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T14:24:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Gpa 3 頭 係咪唔洗諗入番ugc ? Ive商科</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNo, IVE 898</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n入比你睇 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n賭定j先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 入到我切呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d01db70f1032eef6f0919a986df387c13c3f5ba","tid":43913,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T14:59:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Gpa 3 頭 係咪唔洗諗入番ugc ? Ive商科</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNo, IVE